[I] Qt6 API and tools for the Quick shader pipeline

[T] APIs and tools in this module provide the producer functionality for the
[T] shader pipeline that allows Qt Quick to operate on Vulkan, Metal, and
[T] Direct3D, in addition to OpenGL.

